{
  "chapter": 111,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述项少龙精心策划的邯郸大战收网阶段。首先设计擒获赵明雄，以放其家人出城为条件换取合作，重新控制北门。随后在城中各处布下天罗地网，由成胥、滕翼等分头行动，擒下甘竹、李明、赵令等叛将。赵霸负责围困侯府，项少龙率精兵团由水道潜入侯府，在蒲布的内应配合下，攻入内府生擒赵穆。善柔亲手制服仇人赵穆，报了家破人亡之恨。项少龙撕下假面具揭露真实身份后，众人经地道撤出，放火焚烧侯府制造假象，由北门出城西去秦国。全章高潮迭起，展现了项少龙运筹帷幄的军事才能。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董将军！这是怎么回事？下属并没有犯错。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "与赵穆勾结齐人，密谋造反，算不算犯错？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "你们莫要诬害我！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "你的官署下面新近建成一条宏伟的地道，赵明雄你不会说不知道吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把他绑起来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "若你肯乖乖和本城守合作，我会放你一条生路，送你与家人逃出城外。若我有一字虚语，教董马痴不得好死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "但你须把与赵穆通讯的方法交代清楚，只要我们发觉所言属实，立即让你由东门逃出城外，还赠予粮食、马匹和通行关文，人来！给我开门。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大恩不言谢，小人服哩！无论董城守有任何吩咐，小人无不遵从。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "立即放了赵兄！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先把赵夫人、公子等送上马车，护往城外密林处，不得无礼，以免惊吓了夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "这几天邯郸自顾不暇，只要赵兄连夜赶程，离开赵境，定可安度余年，赵兄该不用本人教你怎么办吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人当知无不言，言无不尽。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "甘竹、李明、赵令等三人均被成胥率领禁军擒下，现在全城已在我们掌握里。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "现在本城守会使人护送赵兄出城与家人会合，当第一枝讯号火箭冲上天空时，我的人自会放赵兄离去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "赵明雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不能在董将军帐下用命，实是赵明雄一生人最大的遗憾。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ming_xiong",
      "text": "赵兄保重了，一路顺风。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董将军的奇谋妙计，令嫣然大开眼界，钦佩不已。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "这人不过有点鬼门道，嫣然哪须佩服得他五体投地的样儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "馆主你好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一切部署妥当，侯府已被重重围困，保证半个人都走不掉。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "进攻侯府的事，交由馆主全权负责，当第一枝讯号火箭在城北射上天上时，赵穆的人将会倾巢而出，与齐人分头攻打王宫，那时才予他迎头痛击。但无论形势如何发展，未见我发出约定的火箭讯号，亦切勿攻打侯府，因为我奉有大王之命，要亲身潜入府内，生擒赵穆这个奸贼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今夜的口令由'秦人必败'改作'吾王万岁'，切勿放过敌人，好了！时间差不多，让我们戴起标记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小俊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "城守请吩咐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们准备好两架攻城车，保证几下子即可撞破赵穆的围墙，那时他们想死守都办不到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_bu",
      "speaker_name": "蒲布",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "赵穆中计哩！一点不知道外间发生了什么事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_pu_bu",
      "text": "他会否亲自率人进攻王宫呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_bu",
      "speaker_name": "蒲布",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这胆小鬼怎敢亲身犯险，否则不用龟缩在后宅处，那里有秘道可逃出府外。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_pu_bu",
      "text": "水道出口那边是否有人把守？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_bu",
      "speaker_name": "蒲布",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "所有人全集中到广场处，准备攻打王宫，现在池塘旁完全没有人把守。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_pu_bu",
      "text": "各位兄弟情况如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_bu",
      "speaker_name": "蒲布",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们都晓得怎样应变的了，最妙是赵穆把他们编成一组，由我和刘巢指挥，进退均非常容易。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "齐人的先头部队来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "纪才女有否想过要陪我项少龙钻水渠呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上刀山、落枪坑全都没有问题，何况只是舒服地钻地洞。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该轮到我们哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快点！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不准杀害婢仆妇孺，蒲布领路，去吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "奸贼认得本姑娘是谁吗？我就是齐国善大夫之女，记得你害得我家破人亡吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷别来无恙？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡你好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我并不是董匡！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王卓！我早知你是见利忘义的卑鄙之徒！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我也不是王卓！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "依计行事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "当日你奸杀我项少龙的女人时，曾否想过有今朝一日？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找到地道的入口了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你先行一步，探清楚没有问题，我们才来，还不脱下面具。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我想杀赵穆。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看你的样子，人家只是吓唬你来玩儿的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷真有心，还有闲情来探望我们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们守稳城门，我带人出去搜捕敌人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人聚齐了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让我们回家吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 387
    }
  ],
